info.name: Strawberry Pastry
info.description: Serves 4 | The perfect treat for berry season! Our set of 1 Strawberry Pastry is layered with freshly made strawberry compote, creating an irresistible dessert to satisfy your sweet cravings. Savor the season's favorite, complemented by a delightful twist of vanilla.

info.name: Chocolate Snicker Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Our signature chocolate cake base is layered with rich chocolate cream, homemade chocolate ganache, and blended molten Snickers chocolate, finished with a peanut praline sauce.

info.name: Red Velvet Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A rich sponge is layered with cream cheese whipped cream and dusted with velvet sponge crumbs. There are no artificial colors; the red velvet uses beetroot for color. This is the original Red Velvet recipe that originated in the United States.

info.name: Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with vanilla whipped cream and dark cherry compote, then finished with dark chocolate shavings and red cherries. It’s a classic Black Forest recipe.

info.name: German Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Multiple layers of German dark chocolate sponge are topped with light chocolate cream, vanilla cream, and infused with dark and sour cherry compote. It is finished with a cherry and choco curls. The darker, more sour cherries make it an authentic German Black Forest cake recipe.

info.name: Blueberry Bake Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | A light and creamy cheesecake slice made with cream cheese and topped with blueberry compote.

info.name: Chocolate Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with chocolate ganache and topped with chocolate sponge crumbs.

info.name: Red Velvet Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | This jar cake features a sponge infused with natural beetroot color and cream cheese frosting, along with red velvet crumbs. We have recreated the original recipe that originated in the United States.

info.name: Valentine Day Special Choco Truffle Poster Cake (500gm)
info.description: Serves 6 | Make your Valentine’s Day unforgettable with our Choco Truffle Poster Cake (500gm) – a rich, indulgent chocolate cake topped with a edible poster. A perfect way to celebrate love!

info.name: Valentine Day Special Butterscotch Poster Cake (500gm)
info.description: Serves 6 | Celebrate Valentine’s Day with our Butterscotch Poster Cake (500gm) – a smooth, creamy butterscotch cake topped with a edible poster. The sweetest way to express your love!

info.name: Valentines Special Butterscotch Bento Cake (300 gm)
info.description: Serves 4 | Celebrate love with our Valentine's Special Butterscotch Bento Cake (300 gm). This decadent cake features a rich butterscotch flavor, perfectly paired with smooth, creamy frosting. Encased in a cute bento box, it's an irresistible treat to share with someone special this Valentine's Day!

info.name: Valentine's Special Choco Truffle Cake with topper (500g)
info.description: Serves 6 | Celebrate love with our Valentine's Special Choco Truffle Cake (500g), featuring rich, velvety chocolate layers and a smooth truffle glaze, elegantly finished with a cute cake topper.

info.name: Valentine's Special Choco Truffle Cake (500g)
info.description: Serves 6 | Celebrate love with our Valentine’s Day Special Choco Truffle Cake—moist chocolate sponge, rich truffle ganache, and heart-shaped decorations for the perfect sweet indulgence.

info.name: Valentine's Special Red Velvet Cake with topper (500g)
info.description: Serves 6 | Make your Valentine’s celebration extra special with our Red Velvet Cake (500g), featuring soft, velvety layers, luscious cream cheese frosting, and a romantic topper for the perfect finishing touch.

info.name: Valentine's Special Red Velvet Cake (500g)
info.description: Serves 6 | Celebrate love with our Valentine's Special Red Velvet Cake—velvety smooth layers of rich red cake, cream cheese frosting, and a hint of sweetness, perfect for sharing!

info.name: Valentine Day Special Chocolate Jar Cake - Set of 2 (180ml each)
info.description: Serves 4 | Sweeten your Valentine’s Day with our Special Chocolate Jar Cakes – a set of 2 (180ml each) decadent chocolate cakes, layered with creamy frosting. The perfect treat for your special someone!

info.name: Single Red Rose
info.description: Serves 1

info.name: Strawberry Bake Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | Featuring a creamy cheesecake layer atop a buttery biscuit base, crowned with a vibrant strawberry compote, this dessert is a harmonious blend of sweetness and tanginess. A slice of perfection for strawberry lovers!

info.name: Strawberry Jar Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Indulge in layers of pure bliss with our Strawberry Jar Cake! Featuring moist sponge cake, luscious strawberry compote, and velvety whipped cream, all beautifully assembled in a charming jar. This delightful treat is perfect for savoring the flavors of strawberry season anytime, anywhere!

info.name: Choco Vanilla Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A four-layer vanilla sponge cake is layered with chocolate truffle, topped with a vanilla glaze and dark chocolate truffle. The cake is finished with a white chocolate garnish and a cherry.

info.description: Serves 1 | This cake produces a marble-like texture and pattern by swirling together rich vanilla and chocolate batters. It is topped with a white chocolate glaze, a cherry, and double chocolate nibs.

info.name: Fresh Fruit Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A vanilla sponge base is topped with freshly whipped vanilla custard cream and an assortment of thinly sliced seasonal fresh fruits. It is finished with vanilla cream and toasted almond flakes, which give it a subtle almondy aftertaste.

info.name: Vanilla Blueberry Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Our classic vanilla base is layered with fresh blueberry compote and vanilla cream, topped with whipped cream and garnished with white chocolate.

info.name: Red Velvet Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A rich sponge is layered with cream cheese whipped cream and dusted with velvet sponge crumbs. There are no artificial colors; the red velvet uses beetroot for color. This is the original Red Velvet recipe that originated in the United States.

info.name: Butterscotch Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A vanilla sponge cake is layered with fresh caramel cream and butterscotch crumble, then finished with caramel glaze and cake crumb dressing on the sides. It’s a classic butterscotch recipe.

info.name: Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | A dark chocolate sponge cake is layered with vanilla whipped cream and dark cherry compote, then finished with dark chocolate shavings and red cherries. It’s a classic Black Forest recipe.

info.name: German Black Forest Cake
info.description: Serves 1 | Multiple layers of German dark chocolate sponge are topped with light chocolate cream, vanilla cream, and infused with dark and sour cherry compote. It is finished with a cherry and choco curls. The darker, more sour cherries make it an authentic German Black Forest cake recipe.

info.name: Trio Mousse Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | This gourmet cake features three layers of mousse - milk chocolate, white chocolate, and dark chocolate. The top layer is made of chocolate truffle and is garnished with a golden leaf and a milk chocolate decoration. This recipe originated in Europe.

info.name: Nutella Hazelnut Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge base is layered with chocolate hazelnut mousse, dark chocolate, milk chocolate fresh cream, and molten Nutella.

info.name: Belgian Chocolate Cake (600 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A chocolate sponge base is layered with dark chocolate mousse and a crunchy French biscuit. The cake is topped with a light chocolate drop and a chocolate garnish - a recipe that originated in Europe.

info.name: Coffee Opera Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A square almond sponge base made with eggs and rich chocolate ganache is soaked in filtered coffee syrup and coffee buttercream, then topped with our signature Opera glaze. This recipe is an authentic French classic.

info.name: Tiramisu Cake (500 gm)
info.description: Serves 1 | A sponge cake soaked in espresso coffee is layered with mascarpone cheese, topped with freshly whipped cream, and dusted with cocoa. This dessert is infused with a hint of alcohol and is a perfect choice to sweeten any moment. This is Bakingo’s rendition of a classic Italian tiramisu recipe.

info.name: New York Bake Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | Cheesecake made with high concentration of cream cheese with dense and rich texture. A recipe originated in USA.

info.name: Blueberry Bake Cheesecake Slice

info.name: Biscoff Baked Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | A classic Belgian Biscoff cheesecake in slice form. The cheese base is topped with Biscoff spread and infused with a Lotus Biscoff biscuit.

info.name: Nutella Cheesecake Slice
info.description: Serves 1 | Cheesecake crafted with cream cheese and topped with Nutella - a dreamy combination come true.

info.description: Serves 1 | A fusion of cheesecake, chocolate, and Oreos that results in a unique dessert - a true innovation from Bakingo.

info.name: Blueberry Baked Cheesecake (600 gm)

info.name: Biscoff Baked Cheesecake (600 gm)

info.description: Serves 1 | A vanilla sponge base is soaked with espresso syrup, topped with mascarpone cream cheese frosting and freshly whipped cream, then dusted with Belgian cocoa powder. This dessert is infused with a hint of alcohol and is a perfect choice to sweeten any moment. Italy’s national dessert
